│ AI Integration Architecture                                                                                                   │
│                                                                                                                               │
│ Service Layer (app/Services/Ai/)                                                                                              │
│                                                                                                                               │
│ All AI services follow the same pattern:                                                                                      │
│ - Constructor accepts model name (from config/ai.php)                                                                         │
│ - execute() method with typed params, returns structured result                                                               │
│ - Tracks interaction in ai_interactions table                                                                                 │
│ - Uses Laravel AI SDK (Laravel\AI\Facades\AI) with structured output                                                          │
